cold-blooded nature. Consider this:

67
00:05:53,460 --> 00:05:55,740
Four bullets per victim.

68
00:05:56,460 --> 00:05:58,100
Not six shots fired, but eight.

69
00:05:58,580 --> 00:06:02,060
