the gun empty...

70
00:06:02,260 --> 00:06:04,100
...and then stopped to reload...

71
00:06:04,340 --> 00:06:07,700
...so that he could shoot
each of them again.

72
00:06:07,860 --> 00:06:10,340
An extra bullet per lover...

73
00:06:11,060 --> 00:06:12,740
...right in the head.

74
00:06:16,140 --> 00:06:20,740
You strike me as a particularly icy
and remorseless man, Mr. Dufresne.

75
00:06:21,100 --> 00:06:23,140
It chills my blood just to look at you.

76
00:06:25,020 --> 00:06:27,660
By the power vested in me
by the state of Maine...

77
00:06:27,860 --> 00:06:31,980
...I hereby order you to serve
two life sentences back-to-back...

78
00:06:32,300 --> 00:06:34,740
...one for each of your victims.
So be it!

79
00:06:58,860 --> 00:06:59,980
