1026
01:17:57,800 --> 01:17:59,680
Woman can't bake worth shit.

1027
01:18:00,840 --> 01:18:02,160
Thank you, sir.

1028
01:18:04,880 --> 01:18:07,960
He's got his fingers
in a lot of pies, from what I hear.

1029
01:18:08,160 --> 01:18:12,800
He's got scams you haven't even
dreamed of. Kickbacks on his kickbacks.

1030
01:18:13,000 --> 01:18:15,280
