running through here.

1031
01:18:15,480 --> 01:18:19,160
Sooner or later, he'll have to
explain where it came from.

1032
01:18:19,320 --> 01:18:21,040
That's where I come in.

1033
01:18:21,600 --> 01:18:23,800
I channel it. Filter it. Funnel it.

1034
01:18:24,000 --> 01:18:26,720
Stocks, securities,
tax-free municipals.

1035
01:18:27,040 --> 01:18:30,440
I send it out into the real world,
and when it comes back....

1036
01:18:30,600 --> 01:18:33,440
-Clean as a virgin's honeypot, huh?
-Cleaner.

1037
01:18:34,040 --> 01:18:37,480
By the time Norton retires,
I'll have made him a millionaire.

1038
01:18:39,760 --> 01:18:43,880
If they ever catch on, he'll wind up
in here wearing a number himself.

1039
01:18:44,160 --> 01:18:46,720
