was getting ready to take his exams...

1151
01:24:47,200 --> 01:24:49,280
...it was lovely Raquel.

1152
01:25:05,160 --> 01:25:06,120
Time.

1153
01:25:11,920 --> 01:25:12,880
Well?

1154
01:25:14,400 --> 01:25:16,480
Well, it's for shit.

1155
01:25:16,960 --> 01:25:19,680
I wasted a whole year
of my time with this bullshit.

1156
01:25:19,840 --> 01:25:21,320
It's probably not that bad.

1157
01:25:21,520 --> 01:25:25,560
I didn't get a thing right.
It might as well have been in Chinese.

1158
01:25:25,760 --> 01:25:27,400
