1159
01:25:27,600 --> 01:25:30,440
I'll tell you
how the goddamn score comes out.

1160
01:25:32,320 --> 01:25:33,640
Two points, right there!

1161
01:25:33,840 --> 01:25:35,320
There's your goddamn score!

1162
01:25:35,560 --> 01:25:39,080
Goddamn cats crawling up trees,
5 times 5 is 25....

1163
01:25:40,000 --> 01:25:41,560
Fuck this place!

1164
01:25:41,800 --> 01:25:42,880
Fuck it!

1165
01:26:01,240 --> 01:26:02,440
I feel bad.

1166
01:26:02,680 --> 01:26:03,800
I let him down.

1167
01:26:04,000 --> 01:26:05,680
That's crap, kid.

1168
01:26:05,840 --> 01:26:07,120
He's proud of you.

1169
01:26:07,480 --> 01:26:10,200
We're old friends,
I know him as good as anybody.

1170
01:26:10,400 --> 01:26:11,880
Smart fellow, ain't he?

1171
01:26:12,120 --> 01:26:15,120
Smart as they come.
He was a banker on the outside.

1172
01:26:15,280 --> 01:26:17,440
What's he in here for anyway?

1173
01:26:17,760 --> 01:26:18,680
Murder.

1174
01:26:20,080 --> 01:26:21,400
The hell, you say.

1175
01:26:23,480 --> 01:26:25,680
You wouldn't think it
to look at the guy.

1176
01:26:26,880 --> 01:26:30,800
Caught his wife in bed
with some golf pro. Greased them both.

1177
01:26:38,520 --> 01:26:39,480
