1179
01:26:43,440 --> 01:26:46,560
...I was in Thomaston
on a two-to-three stretch.

1180
01:26:47,040 --> 01:26:48,280
I stole a car.

1181
01:26:48,640 --> 01:26:50,560
It was a dumb-fuck thing to do.

1182
01:26:51,200 --> 01:26:53,360
About six months left to go...

1183
01:26:53,600 --> 01:26:55,440
