1184
01:26:56,120 --> 01:26:57,680
Elmo Blatch.

1185
01:26:58,360 --> 01:26:59,640
Big, twitchy fucker.

1186
01:27:00,480 --> 01:27:03,800
Kind of roomie you pray you don't get.
