1187
01:27:04,000 --> 01:27:06,640
Six-to-twelve, armed burglary.

1188
01:27:06,920 --> 01:27:09,080
Said he pulled hundreds of jobs.

1189
01:27:09,280 --> 01:27:14,040
Hard to believe, high-strung as he was.
You cut a loud fart, he jumped three feet.

1190
01:27:15,040 --> 01:27:19,480
Talked all the time too. That's
the other thing. He never shut up.

1191
01:27:19,680 --> 01:27:21,240
Places he'd been in...

1192
01:27:21,560 --> 01:27:24,440
...jobs he'd pulled, women he fucked.

1193
01:27:24,680 --> 01:27:26,800
Even people he killed.

1194
01:27:28,000 --> 01:27:30,680
People who "gave him shit."

1195
01:27:31,280 --> 01:27:32,800
That's how he put it.

1196
01:27:35,280 --> 01:27:37,280
So one night, like a joke...

1197
01:27:38,360 --> 01:27:41,680
...I say to him,
"Elmo, who did you kill?"

1198
01:27:41,920 --> 01:27:42,960
So he says:

1199
01:27:43,160 --> 01:27:46,960
I got me this job one time,
busing tables at a country club...

1200
01:27:47,640 --> 01:27:51,360
...so I could case all these big
rich pricks that come in.

1201
01:27:53,400 --> 01:27:55,320
So I pick out this guy...

1202
01:27:56,160 --> 01:27:57,640
