1237
01:29:51,520 --> 01:29:54,040
Don't make it mine.
This meeting is over.

1238
01:29:54,240 --> 01:29:56,720
If I got out, I'd never mention
what happens here.

1239
01:29:57,320 --> 01:30:00,200
I'd be as indictable as you
for laundering that money.

1240
01:30:01,960 --> 01:30:04,800
Don't ever mention money to me,
you son of a bitch!

1241
01:30:05,000 --> 01:30:06,560
Not in this office...

1242
01:30:06,760 --> 01:30:08,640
