Get in here, now!

1243
01:30:08,880 --> 01:30:11,440
I just wanted to put you at ease,
that's all.

1244
01:30:12,080 --> 01:30:13,280
Solitary. A month.

1245
01:30:14,240 --> 01:30:15,480
What's wrong with you?

1246
01:30:15,680 --> 01:30:16,920
Get him out of here.

1247
01:30:17,120 --> 01:30:18,600
