1253
01:30:30,720 --> 01:30:32,240
Bullshit.

1254
01:30:32,880 --> 01:30:35,480
You didn't pull the trigger
or convict him.

1255
01:30:35,680 --> 01:30:38,000
Are you saying Andy is innocent?

1256
01:30:38,200 --> 01:30:40,120
I mean, for real innocent?

1257
01:30:40,320 --> 01:30:41,600
It looks that way.

1258
01:30:42,040 --> 01:30:43,840
Sweet Jesus.

1259
01:30:44,080 --> 01:30:45,840
How long has he been here now?

1260
01:30:46,240 --> 01:30:49,400
1 947. What is that?
Nineteen years.

1261
01:30:49,600 --> 01:30:52,080
-Williams, Thomas.
-Yeah, over here.

1262
01:30:57,720 --> 01:30:58,840
